Roseline Adebimpe Adewuyi bụ onye nkuzi mmekọrịta ọha na eze na Naịjịria, onye na-akwado okike na onye na-ahụ maka ụmụ nwanyị. N'afọ 2020, ọ so n'ime ụmụ nwanyị iri isii na-eme ihe dị egwu nke BusinessDay Women's Hub gosipụtara na ememe nnwere onwe nke iri isii nke Naịjirịa na onye otu 2018 nke Dalai Lama Fellowship n'ihi ọrụ ya na mmepe nke nwa agbọghọ ahụ.
Adewuyi si Ogbomosho, steeti Oyo gụsịrị akwụkwọ na klas mbụ na French na-enweta nzere Bachelor of Arts na Mahadum Obafemi Awolowo na Masters in Art with Distinction na Mahadim Ibadan.
Ebumnuche Adewuyi bụ iwulite nwa agbọghọ zuru ọke, nke na-adabere n'onwe ya ma na-enyere nwa agbọghọ ahụ aka imebi ụdị echiche nwoke na nwanyị niile.

N'afọ 2018, Adewuyi malitere ide ihe na ebe nrụọrụ weebụ ya kwa izu n'eme ka nsogbu gbasara ụmụ agbọghọ Afrịka pụta ìhè ma na-ahazi mgbasa ozi ụlọ akwụkwọ maka ụmụ agbọghọ nọ n'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị, na-akụziri ha nkà ha chọrọ dị ka ndị isi nwere ike. Ndị National Youth Service rụrụ ọrụ dị ka ntọala nke ọrụ ya ka ọ na-enweta onyinye dị ka onye otu pụrụ iche na Kwara State n'ihi onyinye mmepe obodo ya n'oge afọ ọrụ ya.
Kemgbe ahụ, a họpụtara ya maka mkpakọrịta na mmemme na mba ndị dị ka France, Rwanda, Ethiopia, Ghana, na United States

N'agbata afọ 2019 na 2020, ọ nọ n'ọrụ nke African Union, na-arụ ọrụ dị ka onye ntụgharị French ma nata nkwanye ùgwù gụnyere ịbụ onye otu Commonwealth Youth Gender Equality Network, ONE Champion, MCW fellow, Dalai Lama Fellow, Award for Under 25 years Outstanding Social Innovator in Education by Ideation Hub Africa ma nọchite anya Nigeria na France maka mmemme LabCitoyen Human Rights nke French Embassy kwadoro na Nigeria. Iji mee emume ụbọchị nnwere onwe nke iri isii nke Naịjịria, edepụtara ya dị ka otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị iri isii na-eme ihe dị ịrịba ama site na Business Day Women's Hub.
O nwere akwụkwọ iri n'aha ya.
